
Run book seeder
\\ php artisan db:seed --class=BookSeeder

Wipe everything (Clean slate)
\\ php artisan migrate:fresh

Wipe everything + Re-seed
\\ php artisan migrate:fresh --seed

Wipe only Books
\\ 1. php artisan tinker
\\ 2. Book::truncate();
\\ 3. exit

Undo last migration
\\ php artisan migrate:rollback

Revisions:
1. Add show/hide password field using eye symbol in login & sign up
2. Remove fullname field in sign up
3. Max number in Student ID Number is 9 e.g. 202311074
4. Course and Section should be a selection (Course = BSIT, BSCS, BSEMC) (Year Level = 1, 2, 3, 4) (Block = A-Z)